The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Chemotherapy for Umrigar

Mumbai: Former India Test captain Polly Umrigar underwent chemotherapy here on Thursday. Umrigar underwent chemotherapy on Thursday and it will be continued tomorrow too. 

His condition is stable, a hospital spokesperson said. 

He said since chemotherapy makes a patient weak, Umrigar would remain in the hospital for a few days after the completion of the session. (PTI) 




